{"tid":1412564,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【認真公投】9月罷工週","createTime":"2019-08-05T07:04:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T08:30:42.000Z","uid":216899,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a4a5312b3f0cd4730db6182d25b912f16c613591","tid":1412564,"uid":216899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:04:49.000Z","msg":"林鄭潛水咁耐 一直遊行集會都<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冇出現</span></span>過<br />\n今日一塞交通工具 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">即刻</span></span>朝早出黎開記者會分化<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 點解要至少一星期？</span></span><br />\n一日真係冇乜效用 最多逼到佢開記者會 損失一日經濟<br />\n但至少一星期就唔同了 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">經濟直插水 國際大關注</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">2. 點解今星期唔繼續？</span></span><br />\n罷一星期真係長 需要從長計議 特別係航空業手足<br />\n今日三罷都用左好多時間文宣 罷工週如是咁急進未必係好事<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">3. 點解九月先？</span></span><br />\n政府話中學生大學生唔使返學先咁亂 到時大家慢慢俾佢地搞<br />\n同埋依家好多學生都返緊兼職 始終都要錢生活<br />\n加上好多都發夢發到冇乜錢 可以比佢地玩回血先<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最後 9月罷工週</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反對</span>"},{"pid":"518ba9da47f01e8ae3f7cd34a3b74a58728a273f","tid":1412564,"uid":216899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:05:19.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"475385593e80af8efc7dd75c135aabbd4908e47b","tid":1412564,"uid":216899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:05:39.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"da20cf925a0426cc5ded8e87411526f53574db11","tid":1412564,"uid":216899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:05:55.000Z","msg":"Push"},